20:31.508 --> 20:33.258
I'm fighting again.

20:35.966 --> 20:38.258
- Where you fighting?
- Brooklyn.

20:38.341 --> 20:40.632
It's a bare-knuckle thing.

20:40.715 --> 20:43.174
And I'm about to win it all.

20:44.674 --> 20:46.882
Ter...

20:46.966 --> 20:50.132
- that don't seem too smart.
- Yeah?

20:50.216 --> 20:53.341
You tell me that two fights
away from 50 grand ain't smart?

20:56.715 --> 20:58.715
Ain't that something, huh?

21:01.549 --> 21:03.216
What do you want, Mick?

21:04.715 --> 21:07.007
I, uh, need to talk to Ray.

21:07.966 --> 21:09.924
What's that gotta do
with me?

21:10.007 --> 21:12.924
I need you to call him for me,
set a meet.

21:13.007 --> 21:16.299
If I tell him you're here,
he ain't gonna show.

21:16.383 --> 21:17.882
So don't tell him.

21:20.466 --> 21:23.174
I seen that look before,
Mick.

21:23.258 --> 21:26.091
That's how you used to look
just before you got the belt.

21:26.174 --> 21:27.590
No. No, son.

21:27.674 --> 21:31.424
This is about
mending a fence.

21:31.508 --> 21:34.882
