get things right with everyone.

21:34.966 --> 21:36.632
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

21:36.715 --> 21:38.632
I ain't gonna
call Ray for you.

21:38.715 --> 21:42.132
So you do yourself a favor

21:42.216 --> 21:44.174
and you the fuck out.

21:44.258 --> 21:47.174
♪ tense music ♪

21:47.258 --> 21:50.966
♪♪♪

21:51.049 --> 21:52.258
Ter.

21:52.341 --> 21:57.508
♪♪♪

22:05.966 --> 22:08.882
[sirens wailing distantly]

22:08.966 --> 22:12.924
♪♪♪

22:17.799 --> 22:20.674
[chains jingling,
punches landing]

22:20.757 --> 22:25.924
♪♪♪

22:26.424 --> 22:28.174
[Sandy reading Bible,
Daryll singing over recording]

22:28.258 --> 22:29.590
[Sandy] "No temptation
has overtaken you

22:29.674 --> 22:30.966
