- Man, what you want?

22:51.007 --> 22:53.049
Are you ready to lace 'em up?

22:53.132 --> 22:54.840
What you talking about?

22:54.924 --> 22:56.174
[Mickey] Got a fight tonight.
Big purse.

22:56.258 --> 22:59.840
Just gotta talk to Terry
a little bit.

22:59.924 --> 23:02.549
[Daryll] Pop, I ain't
fighting nobody.

23:02.632 --> 23:04.840
The guy's a tomato can.

23:04.924 --> 23:06.549
Tomato can, my ass.

23:06.632 --> 23:08.508
It's $50,000.

23:08.590 --> 23:10.799
