remember?

23:12.674 --> 23:14.549
[Mickey] Well, uh,
Mexico was a mistake.

23:14.632 --> 23:17.757
Look, I'm not doing it, okay?
I'm a producer now.

23:17.840 --> 23:20.007
- What are you talking about?
- Yo.

23:20.091 --> 23:21.508
