fighting somebody

23:21.590 --> 23:23.049
for, like, 50 grand somewhere.

23:23.132 --> 23:24.341
Give me that.

23:25.299 --> 23:27.715
Mick.

23:27.799 --> 23:29.632
Where are ya?

23:35.508 --> 23:37.466
[Bridget] Hey.

23:37.549 --> 23:39.632
Are you okay?

23:42.299 --> 23:43.840
Um...

23:45.966 --> 23:48.007
