39:25.132 --> 39:27.466
[Terry] Jab.
All right.

39:29.882 --> 39:32.840
Take your time.
Take your time. Go!

39:32.924 --> 39:34.258
- [grunts]
- [Terry] And again!

39:34.341 --> 39:36.424
